2/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpYgm5AJdlzqOpnVbphmc0C9uM0Oy2Kw_mnkl6Wzkpr6FyWvYZ1g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"4 週前\",\"text\":\"千葉火鍋原是我們往年常消費的地方，近年各地區千葉火鍋都升級裝潢，價格也有上漲，新竹忠孝路的尊爵店也在漲價後，就沒光顧。今天慶祝母親節，再度光臨，沒有失望，空間寬敞明亮，菜色也進步很多，螃蟹、蛤、魚片、蝦、牛肉、羊肉⋯⋯各類熟食料理更勝火鍋料理，黃金拉格啤酒喝到飽！！這樣的食材cp值高喔！\",\"time\":1746796438,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"mark chen\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101444570516936950839/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUUeafqO7Iqwn-Md1iPK71T6Nlo0OZOj245svJ6Ic2cmFEDg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":2,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 週前\",\"text\":\"吃飯時間，停車位已經很難找了，吃到一半被叫移動車子，上面寫特約是千葉員工的停車位,才幾個停車位，員工就占了好幾個，感覺…..............\",\"time\":1748441199,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"王馥馨\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102600002959235177840/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVDdpNhcaMCeAPLwk39yhEXEi9Jay1Jc-Z9gismTjRVuL9QprJpag=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":3,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 週前\",\"text\":\"可能是我食量小\\n所以覺得價位有點高😅\\n\\n服務部分很ok\\n環境也很乾淨清爽\\n\\n我吃最多的是豬肉\\n但總感覺粉粉的\",\"time\":1747812722,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"加號\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113811748414198785343/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICRucoqruPgHmE2omj_zFpWqSrG5HScEQ7P_n4DHHfO9fEkmKR=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2\",\"rating\":1,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"超級怪異的店，東西都很不好吃，食材很差，也不新鮮，幾乎壞掉，菜是艘的\\n價位超級不划算，氣氛也怪怪的，\\n懷疑評論是洗的，會送一盤東西\",\"time\":1740568667,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNRXkjiKC5YtB9llTUcwOO2886xt16QLaV26-FCcYIdAn67c86gHPnOtlCG8ToR0p7CHKkBx6qoAFsWuW9TcsyoEly7zaDFWmh6nno2HKnFjScuzlMyWKxOiyMWPP4RlqnFCpvWNuSGX70WfN2