jVNWTWpDsQGLqRtOFSqTBgcRbAQShr_Otju5FLJ3vcTU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 週前\",\"text\":\"每次中午散步經過這家店，總看到店內幾乎是滿座的情況，心想真的這麼好吃嗎？\\n剛好趁著同學聚餐，就來吃看看。\\n原來晚上時間也是幾乎坐滿，環境還可以，餐點也好吃，算不算道地的日本料理，我就不知道了。\",\"time\":1748330155,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"趴趴亂走 的狐狸\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118388211259202782644/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZ0N_hGmvJl863WYKqXcMmqRZHyzEumYedlzC-WAd6Eyom9A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 個月前\",\"text\":\"（4/6）一直記憶在剛開幕時，蒸蛋裡有一小塊帝王蟹。當然那是很久遠前的故事。但免費停車場及透明的落地窗是個不錯的點。\\n主食中規中矩，但附餐就很令人失望，尤其是這樣的價位應該要有合理的自製小菜，而非泛泛的廉價醬菜。\\n餐飲可以續飯續湯，也需要加10%服務費。\",\"time\":1744115247,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"芳芳芳企鵝（72 企鵝）\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104009962723168528975/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXP07wN3et_T7ffuM71eRH_yuHal_2tPuhJJIQweNsXjKIUYDTC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"不錯吃👍🏻 日式定食牛肉奶油燒黑胡椒微辣\\n很下飯～～～\\n杏鮑菇小菜還有加芥末口感很協調好吃😋\\n\\n壽司🍣 口感也不錯😀 煙燻鮭魚捲🤩\",\"time\":1743934835,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Lee lee\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106362108521048371504/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUb0Xch0Su3UdZaZUiWvQDDggchnA6p5j5B6AYknCHUna_-jrQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"鮭魚頭火鍋很不錯，可惜不喜歡魚頭先油炸過。天婦蘿定食，炸金針菇、炸紅蘿蔔？不知道那團是什麼，炸得太油膩了，滿嘴是油。鯖魚定食很不錯，肉質肥美。整體都還不錯\",\"time\":1741595211,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Li Tzu Wang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109219011406387629032/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKTBTXwiyaUBXdgrYbeb-tJzYGatAvtY_OY1XWtTvTBMQyrUc6aw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 個月前\",\"text\":\"海景刺生定食生魚片很多種，沒有腥味～讚\\n配上紫蘇也很好吃！蒸蛋有小蝦仁，整份定食還不錯，不過菜比較少。最後的甜點不會很甜，老少咸宜，適合當作一餐的ending👍\\n定食的飯跟湯都可以續呦！\\n\\n炒高麗菜很好吃～份量不少\\n\\n五仔魚中規中矩\\n\\n綜合壽司蠻多種的，上面的生魚片就像海景定食那樣\\n\\n服務生感覺都做很久了，態度都很客氣，也會積極加水，詢問湯飯有無需要續\\n\\n整體來說還可以，而且有自己的停車場，座位也很多～\\n\\n可惜的是若在尖峰時段，客人很多的時候，廁所會不夠，因為男女廁只有各一間，更何況員工也需要上，這樣偏不方便😢\",\"time\":1733282670,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNTrqPmYTkbjCpDRdlrJ1IbNctkIxhXGrjNVIqFMDZ9imuQjHK1wSh3pFowJWegeCF7XUuH13T9EA2Wv2Nub5p52N8OSCkYpbjJDJm8Yu2IvWuuNimZowMR5_bgV0t5Hs7jHuS7alRVze0G3u9khLxAosgU30IrMK3be-xZl1imgb-8yMqenSt1-WNKmGXeKq2vferNUlPBQkZWUpYU5HaVIBDYiRWfBgEfIEMEarO_W82LAy42RyVWfVlrg8SUYpoO0eLEEVU75ZawKzpyOU9qma8nz_tDE812ywbWIyKIrG_dCrwH6MBz4FewaXfHsM9yf98U1R44-wIqmbUEBPblFqJGlnpKp85urrImLSGBCFB35JEtWSP25JHtKXCalJhuI66-RFOtkJVuHzalyl_cArSEdMok2ogTMijK0kjConajdUdXmi-noFXXdJAaMqvq30pLSoem5ZO2x6EPKuhsvPnw1SidwKAKn3Sb7wuhAK7vmeAY_HBEt7zVd2Y1DliQmuERYxI1JmZm26lKKG5fXLzP2yTnImGHMzhalf7E4uPKZjqLiztO5QsR0bhEKLOOTFVQRcSBR21FETyZDvLHJ-2YhchS4dAacgsnKomYtBHtjsQkXXl3KUyYopCp5MomU0g\",\"AXQCQNQzD_ZMHpK6Tn7u2jthmJmI0LuH_iuMhA3pguNllo_R9pp2LgzPIs2NdqaQrts3vos8_kQLzRFPSIpVpa5IFNpc9HM5QkLC94KNlII0RcklrZEeeCWxBCdjou6WYAqTLIRuZZcJpCyy_SzJ4w8NPGG6xQo2wxcP206wYbA8HnCSeEmv5fsfeUOSQgNpaGQlz6A3ktmcIYmHkikxKcKok4mvXqyWabw00pIDwDNeZNv1BS99VCO91kz3PROp53iFCR6865PlxUGHKuu-kPSUx1pZSUoP_ZSpwwVogRHaSsO14kyszkcy3knvqD9uu52hIYNT2Dh_nXcQF1cm4gSw1eEGY_LxKRC2X3NqxVv5jIhCOovArddCtXSKb9sp7di9vdCuBSiJ4w6U-Wr-2zgn4TBjvIeUMe0U2XtWqJBAdmAnwUWYzZ9pEvSPeejEd6_XS1PJYgDhsZ1RJWgsNjKf1OXibNhBQ-goe6YMB1KQMTN0AJ4gfQOpHpE01FDHVnco3xfc2G1D77JB7KmQrxQ2qolhbHvZvedUpba-nAVEOK767fuDE2VeguiT_razy4BcZcgz717P3Blf4fUyxexYD5E73q97yrFJYLpAWRWNoLIpwZcMpR4KQU2nFlNLtTuUGytu7u1y\",\"AXQCQNRdlibWESv_shNmSj8acSOwGXLgUVL2kH8xDEl5sd6avbIkpuLLPJ5wXJBgn2IrvOCvRi_ak2lwigXacJWvoAHBO2npz_2-S_I9pXEAfkxqE-O9-Hg4tTbXAj76xepu6cmiJ7F8D-2_PrjBtbZQMiCL1bpyLxxHx-gTi5CKHYpkZxNRTSKc-xn1sIUHFNPQO4-YezfyyndbQ5ugk8fOHBp77