0}},{\"start\":{\"hour\":17,\"minute\":0},\"end\":{\"hour\":21,\"minute\":0}}],\"rating\":4.1,\"reviews\":[{\"author_name\":\"皮卡撒\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112885603164804223554/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOE9SK517M-ehdjye5qwqh1qob4mNQRCF_3ez0BBNgUlearA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"1 週前\",\"text\":\"1、CP值不高，你看這個不過蠻多家長帶小朋友去的，但這些小朋友也很秋，一來就跟他爸講說我要吃菲力牛排，直上最貴的，沒在跟他爸客氣\\n2、兩個人吃了$894 ，平均一個人快$500\\n3、門口有停車位，但是都滿的\\n4、自助bar有飯、味噌湯、四種口味的冰淇淋\",\"time\":1748107976,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"エイチョウ\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104455580380683298605/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI3EbcULcXcReX28PIwB_Kgl5642IrdeHZ9QNcBy2_ur3ViHLum=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"3 個月前\",\"text\":\"這次到漢神鐵板燒用餐，整體來說餐點品質還不錯，但用餐體驗有些地方讓人覺得不太值這個價位。首先，這裡的菜品無法免費續加，和一般平價鐵板燒不同，白飯和湯品也無法及時補足，讓食量較大或喜歡搭配白飯的人可能會有點不滿足。\\n\\n坐在吧台區用餐，可以直接看到廚師現場料理，這本來應該是享受鐵板燒的一大特色，但當天卻剛好遇到廚師們在中間吵架，場面有點尷尬，彷彿是高級版的大埔鐵板燒，反而影響了整體的用餐氛圍。\\n\\n店內裝潢與餐具都很講究，看起來確實有高級感，價格自然也不便宜，但如果服務與整體用餐體驗能夠再細緻一點，會更符合這個價位的期待。整體來說，食物不錯，但若想有更愉快的用餐體驗，可能需要挑個氣氛比較好的時段再來。\",\"time\":1740966953,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"CC C\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117488191364512865739/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEwlSy9QMAZt7nHjq4BoD3SoZ82N9eDNiRG2R2zTaDM6FKYA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba8\",\"rating\":4,\"relative_time_description\":\"2 個月前\",\"text\":\"魚肉跟菲力牛好吃，其餘普通，雞腿有點乾柴，豆腐太硬沒入味，高麗菜梗很多，服務不錯\",\"time\":1741870916,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Cynthia Tsai\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116062072949203067937/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV2JyePvmiH4Ex5qpcwAcVxPfHmNr0SKief-wxPEA2KYKuawcZu=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"6 個月前\",\"text\":\"白飯、飲料、湯品、冰淇淋吃到飽\\n常客小知識：可以跟店員要芥末洋蔥（免費提供）\\n青菜用料很足，炒高麗菜紅蘿蔔絲木耳絲跟綠葉菜\\n炒豆芽菜有洋蔥絲跟蘿蘿蔔絲，用料實在\\n湯品的白蘿蔔、玉米、雞肉料也挺多的\\n出餐速度蠻快的，個人覺得調味不算太重鹹\\n低消一個套餐，小朋友共食120元\",\"time\":1731252361,\"translated\":false},{\"author_name\":\"Yu Jie Chiang\",\"author_url\":\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110827460351953452666/reviews\",\"language\":\"zh-Hant\",\"profile_photo_url\":\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVb9pXYKcy3dEOWkjKQgX88tk1fHfmDUUDgwyxIjaKnMfG0d-YI2A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3\",\"rating\":5,\"relative_time_description\":\"8 個月前\",\"text\":\"個人很愛鐵板燒！\\n\\n先說餐廳用餐環境，非常乾淨衛生高雅！\\n\\n餐點的部分\\n\\n配菜：分量剛好，但最讓我意外的是，菜吃起來是脆的而且有菜本身的香氣！\\n\\n主食：黑胡椒牛肉，每個味道都有獨自出現，而且不會太膩口。\\n\\n加價海鮮：牡蠣跟干貝都很新鮮，而且煎的恰到好處，外皮很脆！\",\"time\":1726461388,\"translated\":false}],\"photos\":[\"AXQCQNQYJIWs4SfyfBAPj6IC3CqXd8fp7ugmpHGLIIBC_m5oAybeRK9pJ25MbIPLlnzT5tdXsbrA0JvuZms57HemEpPmrcECkr8cJeOcPpH8U4VBdpwT1xO_hjLSvrsBHWjrMEAsYiiI8gLb17NlIioDwpSHTHH28m7Jko6cp0vLdUykU2u3qpIrW5D8WQGJ8HWW9mCfkbpAOknMfN3fFjVCYYfBMI0BbXpoDTDVgAUnb684NScgVjNjI_irmW_ZQEeabEzERYMhfUWXTjvtVCxe9zo2GJgbmk3c1R944Anif-RgIquR3nQSwVqi8WZ63bUEP3ZVHOxY\",\"AXQCQNQZv312K-0vzj_HkuJ1q9KUiR300y9JpnRjXKQkmgO3IziozcY6k5OoH7rdzrXU2OO0rZjeI3Cc2fRRX8Mbc9gzHF95_KSwN7CWfR-7JjCcTYtRQ4ZExBvIh6tOVk7W89O_iCXO-RlqDbikTyEbjQTN9G1Z7uyqGs6rw7E5wy8A7pqX1h9fzPG_d2_8-TzsMBeDbj_02RVF1a6JXwdCpGM1jl1ykHPLk94D_JYBGHk73x3kkSWbcffVman_ncOQtOg_AnONXpBJ_4qPFYc3pBxbrP8ar1ChFHFHjxW9lFJuEIiNulAVstemUXVt6tjlaJS64bPU\",\"AXQCQNThmuPc2RNnAgsWX9slMS9rTjyN1wt-TW3-uVX4bNC0BH4lN2mzV8Z5HygSaNWwgxvJKnVtWvZw8pWVq5IUim1ykvwelB4291V-xkoTutFlEQbXqQVlZq_XXq8Ai1Q6a3XMLKnyJdBXchNuQMHN058vu-c0PUUUAtFkk97DYXBGmGFy2aXGzNX5_M0AQJZf8OaWUJGmJAVBYfigbo45pfSmpy6310Wa8cmUpZ2Pl2aTXsB5QYoV4SLsKmGHeuJD3Oa0nYKM1URbe-8Tqx0QrKOwFgwgemHaSdFHKNMB16ObHSpHrv4w2fWmGjM9bI5q0TVafItRhHvD_S1MhP7CyQVyPY_r_5QRva8bX6yaH4LvpD89haARN6exKayvi2V2iT0Xf-Q2bzZLEboa4DAMu-C-ybk91tC03TqF99nBWyai4NBvn0